text: Akhmetovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Akhmetovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 886 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Kushnarenkovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Akhmetovo, Kushnarenkovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
